<p>John and Dave take a tour through the Mac OS, discussing how to migrate manually, managing your To-Dos using Mail&#8217;s Smart Mailboxes, changing Skype volume, and some fantastic listener feedback about how Time Machine works and what it&#8217;s doing in the background.  Plus, John and Dave might even share their Macworld Expo predictions! Don&#8217;t miss it.</p>
